"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2022.08-至今<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>长聘副教授，清华大学工程物理系</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2016.08-2022.07<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>准聘副教授，清华大学工程物理系</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2012.12-2016.08<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>副研究员，清华大学工程物理系</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2009.10-2012.11<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>助理研究员，清华大学工程物理系</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2009.03-2009.06<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>访问学者, 美国加州大学洛杉矶分校（UCLA）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2008.02-2008.09<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>访问学者, 美国布鲁克海文国家实验室（BNL）和加州大学洛杉矶分校（UCLA）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2007.09-2009.09<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>博士后，清华大学工程物理系</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2018-至今<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>合讲本科生数理基础课《基础物理学(1)、(2)、(3)》</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2011-至今<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>主讲研究生专业基础课《粒子物理》</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2015-2017<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>合讲本科生数理基础课《普通物理(3)》</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>指导博士毕业生9名，硕士毕业生2名，在读博士生5名</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">高能核物理实验。参加欧洲核子研究中心CERN/LHC对撞机上的LHCb实验、美国BNL/RHIC对撞机上的STAR实验等大型国际合作实验项目，分析重离子碰撞实验数据，研究强相互作用相变和极端高温高密条件下的物质形态。</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>中高能核物理，国家自然科学基金优秀青年基金，2017-2019，负责人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>STAR实验200GeV d+Au碰撞数据奇异粒子产生分析, 国家自然科学基金青年基金, 2010-2012, 负责人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>基于STAR实验的强相互作用性质研究, 教育部全国优秀博士学位论文作者专项资助, 2010-2014, 负责人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>RHIC/STAR实验中重味强子产生数据分析, 中国博士后基金，2008-2010, 负责人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>另作为骨干承担多项基金委重大、重点、国际合作和科技部重点研发课题。</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-decoration: underline;\">代表性</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-decoration: underline;\">学术论文：</span></b></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\">1. “Measurement of the multiplicity dependence of Υ production ratios in pp collisions at </span><img width=\"19\" height=\"41\" src=\"/__local/6/BD/B8/2C6CAB04B74D47BFE43A58BA36F_8CC0A2B2_526.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/6BDB82C6CAB04B74D47BFE43A58BA36F/8CC0A2B2/526\" vheight=\"41\" vwidth=\"19\" orisrc=\"/__local/6/BD/B8/2C6CAB04B74D47BFE43A58BA36F_8CC0A2B2_526.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\"> = 13 TeV”, JHEP 05, 011 (2025), LHCb Collaboration. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 17px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times\">. </span></span><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\">“Observation of strangeness enhancement with charmed mesons in high-multiplicity pPb collisions at </span><img width=\"36\" height=\"41\" src=\"/__local/4/F4/93/400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708_AE9AAFA8_7BE.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/4F493400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708/AE9AAFA8/7BE\" vheight=\"41\" vwidth=\"36\" orisrc=\"/__local/4/F4/93/400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708_AE9AAFA8_7BE.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\"> = 8.16 T</span><span style=\"font-size: 17px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times\">eV</span></span><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\">”, Phys. Rev. D 110, L031105 (2024), LHCb Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\">3. “Multiplicity dependence of </span><img width=\"80\" height=\"41\" src=\"/__local/6/0A/3E/D872DBEC7274DA676BFC5D8ED65_7A844F98_D20.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/60A3ED872DBEC7274DA676BFC5D8ED65/7A844F98/D20\" vheight=\"41\" vwidth=\"80\" orisrc=\"/__local/6/0A/3E/D872DBEC7274DA676BFC5D8ED65_7A844F98_D20.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\"> in pp collisions at </span><img width=\"19\" height=\"41\" src=\"/__local/6/BD/B8/2C6CAB04B74D47BFE43A58BA36F_8CC0A2B2_526.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/6BDB82C6CAB04B74D47BFE43A58BA36F/8CC0A2B2/526\" vheight=\"41\" vwidth=\"19\" orisrc=\"/__local/6/BD/B8/2C6CAB04B74D47BFE43A58BA36F_8CC0A2B2_526.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\"> = 13 TeV”, JHEP 05, 243 (2024), LHCb Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\">4. “Measurement of </span><img width=\"27\" height=\"20\" src=\"/__local/C/B4/64/9FB474D07BEDA221F90AB055461_DE9F333C_804.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/CB4649FB474D07BEDA221F90AB055461/DE9F333C/804\" vheight=\"20\" vwidth=\"27\" orisrc=\"/__local/C/B4/64/9FB474D07BEDA221F90AB055461_DE9F333C_804.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\">-pair production in pp collisions at </span><img width=\"19\" height=\"41\" src=\"/__local/6/BD/B8/2C6CAB04B74D47BFE43A58BA36F_8CC0A2B2_526.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/6BDB82C6CAB04B74D47BFE43A58BA36F/8CC0A2B2/526\" vheight=\"41\" vwidth=\"19\" orisrc=\"/__local/6/BD/B8/2C6CAB04B74D47BFE43A58BA36F_8CC0A2B2_526.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\"> = 13 TeV and study of gluon transverse-momentum dependent PDFs”, JHEP 03, 088 (2024), LHCb Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\">5. “Measurement of prompt </span><img width=\"21\" height=\"20\" src=\"/__local/9/96/C9/07DE7BDAFC75A8E4837C3003DEE_69423AFB_574.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/996C907DE7BDAFC75A8E4837C3003DEE/69423AFB/574\" vheight=\"20\" vwidth=\"21\" orisrc=\"/__local/9/96/C9/07DE7BDAFC75A8E4837C3003DEE_69423AFB_574.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\"> and </span><img width=\"21\" height=\"20\" src=\"/__local/2/EA/6B/134368E9BF142F2B0CDA418E81D_ACEBBA4B_66F.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/2EA6B134368E9BF142F2B0CDA418E81D/ACEBBA4B/66F\" vheight=\"20\" vwidth=\"21\" orisrc=\"/__local/2/EA/6B/134368E9BF142F2B0CDA418E81D_ACEBBA4B_66F.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\"> production in pPb collisions at </span><img width=\"36\" height=\"41\" src=\"/__local/4/F4/93/400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708_AE9AAFA8_7BE.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/4F493400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708/AE9AAFA8/7BE\" vheight=\"41\" vwidth=\"36\" orisrc=\"/__local/4/F4/93/400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708_AE9AAFA8_7BE.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\"> = 5.02 TeV”, JHEP 01, 070 (2024), LHCb Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\">6</span><span style=\"font-size: 17px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times\">. </span></span><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\">“Measurement of the prompt </span><img width=\"19\" height=\"20\" src=\"/__local/D/DE/D1/95B9BC74E08F168BF0488478AD8_45414111_53D.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/DDED195B9BC74E08F168BF0488478AD8/45414111/53D\" vheight=\"20\" vwidth=\"19\" orisrc=\"/__local/D/DE/D1/95B9BC74E08F168BF0488478AD8_45414111_53D.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\"> nuclear modification factor in pPb collisions at </span><img width=\"36\" height=\"41\" src=\"/__local/4/F4/93/400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708_AE9AAFA8_7BE.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/4F493400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708/AE9AAFA8/7BE\" vheight=\"41\" vwidth=\"36\" orisrc=\"/__local/4/F4/93/400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708_AE9AAFA8_7BE.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\"> = 8.16 TeV, Phys. Rev. Lett. 131, 102301 (2023), LHCb Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\">7. “Measurement of sequential </span><img width=\"10\" height=\"20\" src=\"/__local/8/4E/ED/1D62454241D066F8BE534873945_0C40750B_475.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/84EED1D62454241D066F8BE534873945/0C40750B/475\" vheight=\"20\" vwidth=\"10\" orisrc=\"/__local/8/4E/ED/1D62454241D066F8BE534873945_0C40750B_475.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\"> suppression in Au+Au collisions at </span><img width=\"36\" height=\"41\" src=\"/__local/4/F4/93/400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708_AE9AAFA8_7BE.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/4F493400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708/AE9AAFA8/7BE\" vheight=\"41\" vwidth=\"36\" orisrc=\"/__local/4/F4/93/400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708_AE9AAFA8_7BE.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\"> = 200 GeV with the STAR experiment”, Phys. Rev. Lett. 130, 112301 (2023), STAR Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\">8. “Flow and interferometry results from Au+Au collisions at </span><img width=\"36\" height=\"41\" src=\"/__local/4/F4/93/400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708_AE9AAFA8_7BE.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/4F493400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708/AE9AAFA8/7BE\" vheight=\"41\" vwidth=\"36\" orisrc=\"/__local/4/F4/93/400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708_AE9AAFA8_7BE.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\"> = 4.5 GeV”, Phys. Rev. C 103, 034908 (2021), STAR Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\">9. “Strange hadron production in Au+Au collisions at </span><img width=\"36\" height=\"41\" src=\"/__local/4/F4/93/400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708_AE9AAFA8_7BE.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/4F493400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708/AE9AAFA8/7BE\" vheight=\"41\" vwidth=\"36\" orisrc=\"/__local/4/F4/93/400D6A921AF23A76D7C5ABD5708_AE9AAFA8_7BE.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\"> = 7.7, 11.5, 19.6, 27, and 39 GeV”, Phys. Rev. C 102, 034909 (2020), STAR Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\">10. “Bulk Properties of the Medium Produced in Relativistic Heavy-Ion Collisions from the Beam Energy Scan Program”</span><span style=\"font-size: 17px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times\">,</span></span><span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\"> Phy. Rev.</span> <span style=\"font-family: times;font-size: 17px\">C 96, 044904 (2017), STAR Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2019-至今：MPD实验国际合作组“轻味和超核谱”物理工作组召集人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2018-至今：STAR实验国际合作组Council成员</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2012-至今：STAR实验Embedding Coordinator</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2012-2014：STAR实验Light Flavor Spectra物理工作组召集人 </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2010-2012：STAR实验Embedding Deputy</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2025，基础物理学突破奖（作为LHCb合作组成员），Breakthrough Prize基金会</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2015，自然科学奖二等奖（第3完成人），中华人民共和国教育部</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2009, 全国百篇优秀博士论文, 中华人民共